<div class="bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:py-16 lg:px-8">
        <div
            class="px-6 py-6 bg-picton-blue-500 rounded-lg md:py-12 md:px-12 lg:py-16 lg:px-16 xl:flex xl:items-center"
        >
            <div class="xl:w-0 xl:flex-1">
                <h2
                    class="text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-3xl"
                >
                    ¿Quieres recibir nuestras novedades?
                </h2>
                <p
                    class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-6 text-picton-blue-100"
                >
                    Suscríbete a nuestro boletín y recibe las últimas tendencias
                    y ofertas exclusivas.
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="mt-8 sm:w-full sm:max-w-md xl:mt-0 xl:ml-8">
                <form class="sm:flex">
                    <label for="email-address" class="sr-only"
                        >Correo electrónico</label
                    >
                    <input
                        id="email-address"
                        name="email"
                        type="email"
                        autocomplete="email"
                        required
                        class="w-full border-white text-white px-5 py-3 placeholder-gray-100 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-picton-blue-700 focus:ring-white rounded-md"
                        placeholder="Ingresa tu correo electrónico"
                    />
                    <button
                        type="submit"
                        class="mt-3 w-full flex items-center justify-center px-5 py-3 border border-transparent shadow text-base font-medium rounded-md text-picton-blue-600 bg-white hover:bg-picton-blue-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-offset-picton-blue-700 focus:ring-white sm:mt-0 sm:ml-3 sm:w-auto sm:flex-shrink-0"
                    >
                        Suscribirse
                    </button>
                </form>
                <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-picton-blue-100">
                    Nos preocupamos por la protección de tus datos. Lee nuestra
                    <a href="#" class="text-white font-medium underline">
                        Política de Privacidad
                    </a>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
